Steal Vay Hek's Thrax Toxin, mix it, and poison the Infested Boil growing in the center of the plains.

variants.modifierDescription: Eximus units have a much higher spawn rate in this mission. Some of their auras stack.
Only bows may be used in this mission, crossbows however work too! Other weapon types will be removed automatically if equipped.
Any damage received will impart radiation effects, and so will green clouds around the tileset.
